"title": "5381: law, letter and spirit of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5381: law, letter and spirit of",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>A rigid adherence to the letter of the law often masks hypocrisy and neglect of its spirit, namely having God at the centre of one's life and putting others before oneself, or recognising that the law points to Jesus Christ.</p>\n<h2>The letter of the law</h2>\n<h3>Overemphasis on keeping some parts of the law</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark7:1-Mark7:8\">MRK 7:1–7:8</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt15:1-Matt15:2\">MAT 15:1–15:2</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa29:13\">ISA 29:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt9:10-Matt9:13\">MAT 9:10–9:13</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark2:15-Mark2:17\">MRK 2:15–2:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke5:29-Luke5:32\">LUK 5:29–5:32</a></p>\n<h3>Hypocrisy with regard to keeping the law</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark7:9-Mark7:13\">MRK 7:9–7:13</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt15:3-Matt15:6\">MAT 15:3–15:6</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt23:1-Matt23:33\">MAT 23:1–23:33</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke11:37-Luke11:52\">LUK 11:37–11:52</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke18:9-Luke18:14\">LUK 18:9–18:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John9:1-John9:16\">JHN 9:1–9:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom2:17-Rom2:24\">ROM 2:17–2:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa52:5\">ISA 52:5</a></p>\n<h2>The spirit of the law</h2>\n<h3>Jesus Christ and the law</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:17-Matt6:19\">MAT 5:17–6:19</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt19:16-Matt19:30\">MAT 19:16–19:30</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark10:17-Mark10:30\">MRK 10:17–10:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke18:18-Luke18:30\">LUK 18:18–18:30</a></p>\n<h3>Jesus Christ's attitude to the Sabbath</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark2:23-Mark3:6\">MRK 2:23–3:6</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt12:1-Matt12:14\">MAT 12:1–12:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke6:1-Luke6:11\">LUK 6:1–6:11</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark1:21-Mark1:28\">MRK 1:21–1:28</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke4:31-Luke4:37\">LUK 4:31–4:37</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke13:10-Luke13:17\">LUK 13:10–13:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke14:1-Luke14:6\">LUK 14:1–14:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John5:1-John5:16\">JHN 5:1–5:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John7:21-John7:24\">JHN 7:21–7:24</a></p>\n<h3>Jesus Christ's treatment of the woman taken in adultery</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John8:2-John8:11\">JHN 8:2–8:11</a></strong></p>\n<h3>The greatest commandment</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt22:34-Matt22:40\">MAT 22:34–22:40</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark12:28-Mark12:34\">MRK 12:28–12:34</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt25:31-Matt25:46\">MAT 25:31–25:46</a></p>\n<h3>The importance of obedience and right attitudes outweighs that of outward actions</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom2:25-Rom2:29\">ROM 2:25–2:29</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam15:22-1Sam15:23\">1SA 15:22–15:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps51:16-Ps51:17\">PSA 51:16–51:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov21:3\">PRO 21:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa1:11-Isa1:17\">ISA 1:11–1:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer7:21-Jer7:23\">JER 7:21–7:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos6:6\">HOS 6:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos5:21-Amos5:24\">AMO 5:21–5:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic6:6-Mic6:8\">MIC 6:6–6:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal3:1-Gal3:5\">GAL 3:1–3:5</a></p>\n<h3>The spirit of the law is embodied in the new covenant</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor3:3-2Cor3:6\">2CO 3:3–3:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John4:19-John4:24\">JHN 4:19–4:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom7:4-Rom7:6\">ROM 7:4–7:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:1-Rom8:11\">ROM 8:1–8:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:45-1Cor15:46\">1CO 15:45–15:46</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor3:13-2Cor3:18\">2CO 3:13–3:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal5:18\">GAL 5:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb7:18-Heb7:22\">HEB 7:18–7:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb8:1-Heb8:13\">HEB 8:1–8:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer31:31-Jer31:34\">JER 31:31–31:34</a></p>",
